original_title: List of candidates and preferential votes in Sri Lanka 2024 election
original_body_lines: ECONOMYNEXT – Sri Lanka’s 2024 general elections has returned an overwhelming majority of candidates from the National People’s Power of President Anura Dissanayake followed by the Samagi Jana Balwegaya.
The following is a list of reported candidates and preferential votes in the 2024 general election
Compiled based on Rupavahini, Times Online, Ada Derana, and Newswire reports. (Colombo/Nov15/2024)
